<div id="about-the-community" class="section-spacer">
    <h2 class="sect-title">About Hounsfield Heights/Briar Hill</h2>
    <div class="col-grid-2">
        <div>
            <p class="par-lg">Developed on an escarpment, the community offers splendid views of the Rockies on the west and the Downtown on the south.</p>
            <p class="par-xl">The community in Hounsfield Heights/Briar Hill was established in 1953 and has been among the most desirable luxury residential neighborhoods in the city. </p>
            <p class="par-lg">Homes for sale in Hounsfield Heights/Briar Hill are built in a natural setting and comprise primarily of luxurious infill developments with a few upscale apartment condos also available at an average price of $1,710,000.</p>
        </div>
